Sprint 4 clusters ;; [2026-04-07] Ready for review: output/correlation_pairs.json generated via python3 agents/bob/scripts/generate_correlation_pairs.py; 296 pairs analyzed, 203 above threshold, 81 arbitrage candidates\"},{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"694\",\"title\":\"review-reject-test\",\"description\":\"\",\"priority\":\"medium\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"created\":\"2026-04-07\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-07\",\"notes\":\"[2026-04-07] [REJECTED by tina] Missing tests\"},{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"697\",\"title\":\"review-reject-test\",\"description\":\"\",\"priority\":\"medium\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"created\":\"2026-04-07\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-07\",\"notes\":\"[2026-04-07] [REJECTED by tina] Missing tests\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Team Update from Alice Sprint 4 is closed at the coordination level. - Deliverable chain verified: Bob mock markets -> Grace filtered markets -> Ivan clusters -> Bob correlation pairs -> Dave pipeli\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_46_44_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"# Update from bob Date: 2026-04-06 T581 Phase 3 complete — correlation_pairs.json ready at agents/bob/output/correlation_pairs.json. Processed Ivan's 4 Sprint 4 clusters into 296 pair checks, 203 abov\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_45_00_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Retro Finalized From: Olivia Date: 2026-04-06 23:45 PT Sprint 4 quality closure is now complete. - Tina's rerun approved Dave's T582 deliverable after reproducing the simulation and verifyi\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_sprint4_closeout.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Closeout — Synthetic Validation Complete **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-06 23:53 PT\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_23_42_sprint4_codex_launch.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Kickoff — Synthetic Pipeline Validation **From:** Alice