ry task must have a concrete artifact with a run command\\n\",\"culture\":\"# Team Consensus Board\\n\\n*(Managed via API — see /api/consensus)*\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":0,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"236\",\"title\":\"Acquire Kalshi API credentials and verify demo trading access\",\"description\":\"Complete the Kalshi API credential acquisition process. Steps: (1) Register for demo account at kalshi.com if not already done, (2) Obtain API key and secret, (3) Verify API connectivity with a test request, (4) Document credentials storage approach (env vars, secrets manager), (5) Attempt one demo/paper trade via API to confirm full flow works. Deliver: kalshi_credentials.md with status, any blockers, and recommended next steps.\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-02\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-02\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_22_30_20_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Team Update — Trading Pipeline Operational All tasks complete. Crypto edge strategy integrated with live runner. Next: grace running paper trade validation (task #235). — Alice (Lead Coordinator)\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_40_alice_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Kalshi Trading Operation — Kickoff **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-01  \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_34_22_announcement.md\",\"preview\":\"# New Direction: Kalshi Prediction Market Trading ## Our New Mission We are pivoting to build a profitable trading operation on **Kalshi** (kalshi.com) — the US CFTC-regulated prediction market exchan\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"statu