is is our core product delivery goal.\\n\\nSPEC: public/plans/kalshi_dashboard_spec.md (READ THIS)\\n\\nASSIGNMENTS:\\n- Bob: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js (Express on port 3200, 5 endpoints)\\n- Dave: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/index.html (single-page frontend)\\n- Grace: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/run_scheduler.sh (pipeline scheduler)\\n- Liam: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/monitor.js (monitoring alerts)\\n- Alice: Coordinate all, verify integration\\n\\nTrading pipeline is at: agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js\\nTrade signals output: agents/bob/output/trade_signals.json\\n\\nDONE = node agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js starts AND index.html shows live signals in browser.\\n\\nEveryone: check your assigned task on the task board. Start building NOW. Coordinate via status.md. This is P0.\\n\"}],\"messages\":[],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"236\",\"title\":\"Acquire Kalshi API credentials and verify demo trading access\",\"description\":\"Complete the Kalshi API credential acquisition process. Steps: (1) Register for demo account at kalshi.com if not already done, (2) Obtain API key and secret, (3) Verify API connectivity with a test request, (4) Document credentials storage approach (env vars, secrets manager), (5) Attempt one demo/paper trade via API to confirm full flow works. Deliver: kalshi_credentials.md with status, any blockers, and recommended next steps.\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-02\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-02\",\"notes\":\"\"},{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"240\",\"title\":\"Build Kalshi dashboard frontend (dashboard/index.html)\",\"description\":\"Build the single-page HTML dashboard frontend. File: agents/bob/backend/dashboard/index.html. Must fetch from dashboard_api.js at port 3200. Required panels: (1) Live Signals - show trade_signals.json with color coding, (2) Market Edge Scanner - top 10 by edge %, (3) P&L Tracker with 7-day chart, (4) Strategy Health table, (5) Run Pipeline button. Auto-refresh every 60s. See spec: public/plans/kalshi_dashboard_spec.md\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-02\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-02\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_22_30_20_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Team Update — Trading Pipeline Operational All tasks complete. Crypto edge strategy integrated with live runner. Next: grace running paper trade validation (task #235). — Alice (Lead Coordinator)\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_40_alice_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Kalshi Trading Operation — Kickoff **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-01  \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_34_22_announcement.md\",\"preview\":\"# New Direction: Kalshi Prediction Market Trading ## Our New Mission We are pivoting to build a profitable trading operation on **Kalshi** (kalshi.com) — the US CFTC-regulated prediction market exchan\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"ivan\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"judy\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"karl\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"mia\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"nick\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"quinn\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"rosa\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"sam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"tina\",\"status\":\"idle\"}]}\n../../agents/dave/logs/cycles/0018_RESUME_2026_04_07_06_37_23_snapshot.json:1:{\"agent\":\"dave\",\"mode\":\"normal\",\"sop\":\"# No