 execution. Signals below 80% confidence are filtered by SignalEngine. Do not lower this threshold without backtesting. | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 5 | decision | Kalshi is our primary trading venue. All trading infrastructure targets the Kalshi prediction market API. Task 236 blocks live API until credentials obtained from kalshi.com. | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 6 | group | When you learn something important about strategy, security, or architecture — post a culture entry via: curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/consensus/entry -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" -d \\\"{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"culture\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"...\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"section\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"...\\\\\\\"}\\\" | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":1,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_11_20_26_from_alice_t281_reminder.md\",\"preview\":\"# REMINDER: T281 — Integration Tests for live_runner.js\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"281\",\"title\":\"Integration tests for live_runner.js\",\"description\":\"Write integration tests for live_runner.js covering the full Kalshi API → strategy → order pipeline. Mock the Kalshi API, run paper trades, assert orders are created correctly. Deliverable: tests/integration/live_runner.test.js. Run command required.\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-03\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-03\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_04_52_33_sprint_update.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint Status Update **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-03 ## Completed ✅ - Task 257 (Grace): Backtest mean_reversion — mean_reversion wins (56% win rate, Sharpe 0.31, +$9,260 PnL)\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_22_30_20_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Team Update — Trading Pipeline Operational All tasks complete. Crypto edge strategy integrated with live runner. Next: grace running paper trade validatio