 \"title\": \"Sprint 6: Deterministic replay harness for risk controls\",\n    \"description\": \"Following D5/C8: build a replayable execution-path harness that proves stop-loss, capital floor, and order-path behavior against deterministic signal fixtures. Deliver artifact path, run command, freshness marker, and evidence suitable for Tina QA.\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\",\n    \"group\": \"all\",\n    \"assignee\": \"dave\",\n    \"status\": \"in_progress\",\n    \"created\": \"2026-04-07\",\n    \"updated\": \"2026-04-07\",\n    \"notes\": \"[2026-04-07] Activating T817: reviewing replay-harness requirements and current execution path.\",\n    \"notesList\": [\n      \"[2026-04-07] Activating T817: reviewing replay-harness requirements and current execution path.\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"task_type\": \"task\",\n    \"id\": 819,\n    \"title\": \"Sprint 6: Readiness dashboard for artifacts, blockers, and run commands\",\n    \"description\": \"Following D005/C10: publish a lightweight dashboard or report view that surfaces Sprint 6 artifact locations, blocker state, and runnable commands so coordination stays visible while we wait on T236.\",\n    \"priority\": \"medium\",\n    \"group\": \"all\",\n    \"assignee\": \"charlie\",\n    \"status\": \"in_progress\",\n    \"created\": \"2026-04-07\",\n    \"updated\": \"2026-04-07\",\n    \"notes\": \"[2026-04-07] Activated T819 and started dashboard implementation ;; [2026-04-07] Resumed T819; auditing existing dashboard patterns and Sprint 6 artifacts to build readiness view with artifact paths, blocker state, and run commands.\",\n    \"notesList\": [\n      \"[2026-04-07] Activated T819 and started dashboard implementation\",\n      \"[2026-04-07] Resumed T819; auditing existing dashboard patterns and Sprint 6 artifacts to build readiness view with artifact paths, blocker state, and run commands.\"\n    ]\n  }\n]\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
