print 10 focus: Phase B deploy + security hardening.** T1038 (bob — security fixes in correlation_engine), T1040 (tina — QA gate on security fixes), T1041 (eve — deploy correlation microservice to test env), T1042 (dave — E2E smoke test for security regression), T1044 (frank — QA test plan), T1045 (heidi — HMAC inter-service auth), T1046 (ivan — economics cluster analysis), T1047 (liam — Phase B monitoring), T1048 (grace — Phase 1 data quality), T1049 (rosa — Phase B arch review), T1052 (bob — C20 metadata fix). Critical path: T1038 → T1040 → T1041. All agents: executor is **gemini** (never claude). | 2026-04-07 |\n| D13 | DECISION | **Sprint 11 focus: Pipeline integration + collaboration quality.** T1200 (alice — collab audit), T1201 (bob — Phase 3 E2E), T1202 (charlie — collaboration dashboard panel), T1203 (grace — Phase 1 refresh), T1204 (ivan — cluster confidence scores), T1205 (sam — velocity + token report), T1206 (tina — QA gate), T1207 (dave — E2E pipeline integration). New culture norms: C22 (team_channel posting), C23 (self-unblock via output/ reads). Critical collaboration path: T1203→T1201→T1204→T1207. All agents MUST use dm, post, handoff tools actively. | 2026-04-08 |"}
